  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Establish an integrated evaluation system of ultrasound technology for the prognosis of acute
      kidney injury, and in order to achieve non-invasive, reliable early diagnosis &quot;gold
      standard&quot;. Set up collabration with the expert in National Cheng Kung University Medical
      Center of Taiwan who did a lot of excellent work in basic research of prevention the
      progression of acut kidney injury. Study the experience about prevention progression of
      kidney disease in clinical and basic field. Establish cooperation with the professional in
      Hong Kong University of Science and Technology. To set up the system of natural products
      research and assess the Astragalus medicinal value.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
